{"tid":2327483,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"周梓樂死因庭最新發展 當晚A344救護車或較早前較救護隊目所指的時間早 4 分鐘到場","createTime":"2020-12-16T05:51:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T07:55:34.000Z","uid":292499,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8142a3374aae89b76607f490975daa85ba4f2a1e","tid":2327483,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T05:51:32.000Z","msg":"科大生周梓樂死因研訊今（16日）第19日，死因庭先傳召負責為接載梓樂的救護車 A344 安裝行車記錄儀和維修的公司員工，以及藍田消防站消防員出庭作供。根據 A344 行車記錄，救護車A344 於01:17:07 停下。而根據救護隊目早前的證供，A344 於 01:21 才到廣盈閣消防閘外停車，之後步行往停車場接送梓樂。換言之，行車記錄顯示的停車時間，較救護隊目所指早 4 分鐘。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E5%91%A8%E6%A2%93%E6%A8%82%E6%AD%BB%E5%9B%A0%E7%A0%94%E8%A8%8A-%E8%A1%8C%E8%BB%8A%E8%A8%98%E9%8C%84%E5%84%80%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E6%95%91%E8%AD%B7%E8%BB%8A%E5%81%9C%E8%BB%8A%E6%99%82%E9%96%93-%E8%BC%83%E6%95%91%E8%AD%B7%E5%93%A1%E6%89%80%E6%8C%87%E6%97%A9-4-%E5%88%86%E9%90%98/?fbclid=IwAR0ChHimh-1AAjjTDun4I_IH1bG_2wG_TxgBoyCe8RkncPiRNyNybZR6Tq4#.X9mVyiHx8Qs.facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%25A2%2593%25E6%25A8%2582%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%259B%25A0%25E7%25A0%2594%25E8%25A8%258A-%25E8%25A1%258C%25E8%25BB%258A%25E8%25A8%2598%25E9%258C%2584%25E5%2584%2580%25E9%25A1%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E6%2595%2591%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%2581%259C%25E8%25BB%258A%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%2596%2593-%25E8%25BC%2583%25E6%2595%2591%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%2589%2580%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2597%25A9-4-%25E5%2588%2586%25E9%2590%2598%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0ChHimh-1AAjjTDun4I_IH1bG_2wG_TxgBoyCe8RkncPiRNyNybZR6Tq4%23.X9mVyiHx8Qs.facebook&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMUz11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=ff4d69cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%25A2%2593%25E6%25A8%2582%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%259B%25A0%25E7%25A0%2594%25E8%25A8%258A-%25E8%25A1%258C%25E8%25BB%258A%25E8%25A8%2598%25E9%258C%2584%25E5%258